<body>
    <h1>Service now Connector</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>Currently there are 200+ delimiter applications are on boarded i=
n production. Maintaining these files are challenging. after analyzing the =
issue team is decided to create tables and load the data to those tables an=
d replace Delimiter connectors to JDBC.</p>
<p></p>
<p>The service now ticketing process is not changed. When ever provisioning=
 request is created for add remove disable, enable, lock or unlock scenario=
 the service now ticket will be created. once the ticket is closed from ser=
vice now then link is created in sailpoint.</p>
<p></p>
